      "title": "Intake shape factors for entry points in porous media with transversely isotropic hydraulic conductivity",
      "abstract": "The intake shape factors for spherical and disc-shaped entry points located within a hydraulically transversely isotropic porous medium of infinite extent are presented in \\Iexact closed form\\N. Implications of these results on a methodology for the in situ evaluation of the principal hydraulic conductivities are discussed."
